            "Research whether the expert has relationships with organizations that might influence their public statements on the topic."
          ]
        },
        {
          "title": "Verify Accuracy of Attribution",
          "steps": [
            "When possible, check primary sources to confirm the authority actually said what was claimed and in the claimed context.",
            "Be especially cautious with second-hand reports that paraphrase rather than directly quote experts."
          ]
        },
        {
          "title": "Apply Appropriate Weight to Authority",
          "steps": [
