            "Consider expert opinion as one important input among many, not as definitive proof in itself."
          ]
        },
        {
          "title": "Distinguish Between Types of Authority",
          "steps": [
            "Differentiate between epistemic authority (based on knowledge and expertise) and institutional authority (based on position or status).",
            "Remember that holding a position of power or having social status doesn't necessarily confer expertise on technical or scientific matters."
          ]
