    "Is the positive feedback followed quickly by a request or suggestion for a specific action?",
    "Does the affirmation create a sense of being special, chosen, or exceptional compared to others?",
    "Is there a pattern of effusive praise from someone who doesn't know you well enough to make such assessments?",
